we already have.

511
00:28:09.624 --> 00:28:11.492
That's what you guys want.

512
00:28:11.526 --> 00:28:12.893
-Mm-hmm.

513
00:28:17.965 --> 00:28:22.671
-[Cora] <i>I was dating the devil</i>
<i>as a soldier following orders.</i>

514
00:28:22.703 --> 00:28:25.272
