into town tonight.

589
00:33:34.047 --> 00:33:35.482
-Already?

590
00:33:35.517 --> 00:33:37.852
-Mm-hmm.

591
00:33:37.886 --> 00:33:39.319
-Oh. I'm...

592
00:33:41.756 --> 00:33:44.191
[crunches] Mm.

593
