1522
01:16:18.513 --> 01:16:20.448
[groaning]

1523
01:16:20.481 --> 01:16:21.582
-[body thuds]
-[knife clanks]

1524
01:16:21.615 --> 01:16:23.617
-[blood splattering]
-[Chef screaming]

1525
01:16:26.120 --> 01:16:30.658
