[overlapping grunting]

1527
01:16:33.060 --> 01:16:34.028
[man screaming]

1528
01:16:34.061 --> 01:16:35.229
[plate shatters]

1529
01:16:35.262 --> 01:16:36.664
[chair thuds]

1530
01:16:37.465 --> 01:16:40.134
[knife clanking]

1531
01:16:40.167 --> 01:16:41.435
[Elizabeth cackling]

1532
01:16:41.469 --> 01:16:42.837
[plate shatters]

1533
