[music intensifies]

1540
01:17:34.755 --> 01:17:37.091
-I've never seen anything
like that before.

1541
01:17:37.124 --> 01:17:39.760
-No. that was pretty extreme.
[chuckles]

1542
01:17:39.793 --> 01:17:41.729
-Yeah. that wasn't
just a bar fight.

1543
01:17:41.762 --> 01:17:43.764
