1556
01:18:04.218 --> 01:18:05.352
-[Alexis] Mm-hmm.

1557
01:18:12.259 --> 01:18:13.595
-[Ramsey] Hm.

1558
01:18:13.628 --> 01:18:15.029
Sure is a beautiful night.

1559
01:18:17.164 --> 01:18:18.132
Look at that moon.

1560
01:18:19.534 --> 01:18:23.572
