where are we going?

1562
01:18:26.240 --> 01:18:28.375
-I just thought we needed
to calm down a bit

1563
01:18:28.409 --> 01:18:29.743
after all that.

1564
01:18:30.711 --> 01:18:33.280
This place is beautiful here.

1565
01:18:34.815 --> 01:18:37.619
What could be mellower
than here. right?

1566
01:18:37.652 --> 01:18:40.487
